headline: The Quest to Make the Perfect Toothbrush
summary: A-HED Eduardo Jiménez has thousands of toothbrushes. He compliments strangers on their smiles, then asks them about their dental regime. Family and friends know not to get him started about their oral habits because he may not stop.
